Title: Sugar
Artist: Flo Rida Ft. Wynter
Album: R.O.O.T.S.
Year: 2009



"Sugar is the 3rd official single from Flo Rida's sophomore album R.O.O.T.S., following the success of Right Around and promo single Shone, Sugar turns out to be a exotic and colorful video.

The video first starts with Flo Rida entering a dentist office. She (the dentist) gasses him and Flo Rida finds himself in a dream, on a beach with mysterious SUGAR things happening. The video also shows Wynter singing and dancing with 2 back-up dancers."
